---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
import { SITE_DESCRIPTION, SITE_TITLE } from '../consts';
---

<Layout title={SITE_TITLE} description={SITE_DESCRIPTION}>
	<div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-4 py-12">
		<div class="text-center mb-12">
			<h1 class="text-4xl md:text-6xl font-bold text-white mb-6">
				üßë‚ÄçüöÄ Hello, Astronaut!
			</h1>
			<p class="text-xl text-gray-300 max-w-2xl mx-auto">
				Welcome to the official <a href="https://astro.build/" class="text-blue-400 hover:text-blue-300">Astro</a> blog starter template. This
				template serves as a lightweight, minimally-styled starting point for anyone looking to build
				a personal website, blog, or portfolio with Astro.
			</p>
		</div>

		<div class="bg-gray-900 rounded-lg shadow-xl p-8 mb-8">
			<p class="mb-6">
				This template comes with a few integrations already configured in your
				<code class="bg-gray-800 text-blue-300 px-2 py-1 rounded">astro.config.mjs</code> file. You can customize your setup with
				<a href="https://astro.build/integrations" class="text-blue-400 hover:text-blue-300">Astro Integrations</a> to add tools like Tailwind,
				React, or Vue to your project.
			</p>
			
			<h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-white mb-4">Getting Started Ideas:</h2>
			<ul class="space-y-3 text-gray-200">
				<li class="flex items-start">
					<span class="text-blue-400 mr-2">‚Ä¢</span>
					Edit this page in <code class="bg-gray-800 text-blue-300 px-2 py-1 rounded">src/pages/index.astro</code>
				</li>
				<li class="flex items-start">
					<span class="text-blue-400 mr-2">‚Ä¢</span>
					Edit the site header items in <code class="bg-gray-800 text-blue-300 px-2 py-1 rounded">src/components/Header.astro</code>
				</li>
				<li class="flex items-start">
					<span class="text-blue-400 mr-2">‚Ä¢</span>
					Add your name to the footer in <code class="bg-gray-800 text-blue-300 px-2 py-1 rounded">src/components/Footer.astro</code>
				</li>
				<li class="flex items-start">
					<span class="text-blue-400 mr-2">‚Ä¢</span>
					Check out the included blog posts in <code class="bg-gray-800 text-blue-300 px-2 py-1 rounded">src/content/blog/</code>
				</li>
				<li class="flex items-start">
					<span class="text-blue-400 mr-2">‚Ä¢</span>
					Customize the blog post page layout in <code class="bg-gray-800 text-blue-300 px-2 py-1 rounded">src/layouts/BlogPost.astro</code>
				</li>
			</ul>
		</div>

		<div class="text-center">
			<p class="text-gray-300 mb-4">
				Have fun! If you get stuck, remember to
				<a href="https://docs.astro.build/" class="text-blue-400 hover:text-blue-300">read the docs</a>
				or <a href="https://astro.build/chat" class="text-blue-400 hover:text-blue-300">join us on Discord</a> to ask questions.
			</p>
			<p class="text-gray-400">
				Looking for a blog template with a bit more personality? Check out
				<a href="https://github.com/Charca/astro-blog-template" class="text-blue-400 hover:text-blue-300">astro-blog-template</a>
				by <a href="https://twitter.com/Charca" class="text-blue-400 hover:text-blue-300">Maxi Ferreira</a>.
			</p>
		</div>
	</div>
</Layout>
